summary: An Ordinance authorizing the Mayor and City Comptroller to issue Local Improvement Bonds for the improvement of Twenty-third Avenue West from the intersection of West Garfield Street to West Newton Street in the City of Seattle, by constructing, a bridge roadway to under Ordinance No. 26851, creating Local Improvement District No. 2482 prescribing the rate of interest thereon and authorizing their delivery to the contractor constructing the improvement.
